values:
On saturday i went to OMSI with my cousins! we went on the submarine, there was a really weird guy on our tour! we also went on the virtual rollercoaster! yesterday for my grandmas 80th birthday me, my cuzins, and my sister got our own limo for 5 hours! my aunt uncle and parents and grandma got another... we had to go to portland city grill for dinner until like 8 but then we picked up some of my sisters friends and Kelsey! we went to coldstone and got icecream! then the limo man drove us around for a while until he dropped me and Kelsey off at Katies house!!! Kelsey and I slept over at Katie's house with Beth!  We baked a cake, took a lot of pictures, watched Lord of the Rings, and just talked and hung out! it was a lot of fun!!!  Later today, at 5 I'm going over to Caroline's house and we are going to watch IT!!!  I haven't seen it but Caroline said it is really scary!  But until then I have to finish my homework, or I cant go!  I also want to update my webshots! so look at them!

<3!!

hey hey!  my cousins are here, so that pretty much takes up my weekend!  tommarow me, peter, paul, stephanie, my aunt, uncle, mom, dad, and grandma are going out to dinner at portland city grill for my grandmas 80th birthday... it should be pretty fun, were taking two limos... 1 for the kids and 1 for the rest of them, and after dinner we get to ride around for awhile!  My mom was a little bit mad at me today because i went to the play instead of out to dinner with them, so tommarow im spending the entire day with them at OMSI, it actually sounds kinda fun though... eh not really!  I saw the play again tonight! it was fun! everybody (once again!) did soooo good!  Katie, Beth, and Kelsey are supposed to call me soon!  I remembered what i had to tell katie and now im really excited to tell her! but shes not calling me yet so im getting frusterated... i think i might just call her... 

BETH LOOKS SO PRETTY IN MY WEBSHOT PICTURES! but she made me take them out... and she KNOWS she looks adorable in them too!!!

ooo i forgot! on Sunday at 5 Beth and I are going to Carolines house! too watch "IT!" AND "IT 2!" im so excited!  ive been wanting to see taht movie for sooo damn long! 

<3

i went to annie yesterday and everybody did really good!  i think im going again on friday with kelsey but idk yet... i went home at break today because i didnt feel good, i slept until 1 then went out with my mom to run arands because the cleaning people came...  and i watched mary kate and ashley movies our lips are sealed... i love that movie! now im feeling beter iu think im going to school tommarow... 

<3

Today was pretty fun!  I got new jeans, Alex and I traded, so now I have her It Jeans and she has my Hydraulics!  We traded outfits too, but I want my shirt back, and I'm giving her back her sweat shirt thing...


Hunter!  I'm so sorry!


I got an A on my science project and that was pretty fun!


Caroline!  Feel better!


The plays tommarow!  I think I'm going with Kelsey and Alex!



I've got a lot of homework so I'm going to go do it!

Milkshake by Kelis
"My milkshake brings all the boys to the yard And they're like, it's better than yours Damn right it's better than yours I could teach you But I have to charge" You can work it! And you started a new trend or two in 2004!
What 2004 Hit Song Are You?

hey! i got a new live journal name because my old one was weird and i couldnt make it work right... this has been a really fun weekend! on friday i hung out with Kelsey, Beth, Alex, Kate O, and Katie! we went to lunch at applebees and met up with some people there... then we went over to Beths moms house and hung out around there for a while! after that my mom made me come home for a little bit and then I went to a birthday party! it was really fun! well at 830 i left and went over to Kelseys house and we hung out, talked and played truth or dare haha! then we fell asleep really early at like 11 or 12 umm Beth and Katie had to leave early so me and Kelsey went to the mall for awhile, after that i think i went home and i dont remember what i did.  on sunday i went to tennis and my cousins came and we went downtown by the river and ate lunch and hung out i guess, then we came home and like played video games haha it was fun though, they left but there gonna be back on friday for my grandmas 80th birthday! haha! today me Beth and Kelsey went to breakfast around 10 at Bannings!  Beth and Kelsey came over and we curled Beths hair for the play it looks WoNdErFuL haha just kidding it looked horrible... Beth had to go work or something, so after she left Kelsey and I went over to her house... we played basketball with some seventh graders until they like kept trying to get into her house and stuff and Kelsey got really mad, then we went to Talaricos and met up with Mattie, Griffin and Chase B, Katarina and Lily were there too! Mattie, Griffin, and Chase and me and kelsey hung out at westlakebut then we went to matties house and now im home and i just ate dinner! well that was my weekend basicaly! hehe! ive gotta go finish my homework now though!

♥
